                        <p style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 19px; line-height: 1.315789474; margin: 0 0 30px 0;">Thank you for applying to become an AHRC/BBC 2021 New Generation Thinker – we wish you the best of luck.</p>
