                        <p style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 19px; line-height: 1.315789474; margin: 0 0 30px 0;">If you need to get in touch, or have any queries, please email us at: <a href="mailto:support@funding-service.ukri.org">support@funding-service.ukri.org</a>.</p>
